dc_title_s: Hydro (Polygon and Line) Washington County, WI 2014
dc_description_s: These data layers represent hydrography for Washington County, Wisconsin in 2014. It is a feature class within the geodatabase 'Washington_Hydro_2014.gdb'. The feature layers included in this geodatabase are 'Washington_HydroLine_2014' and 'Washington_HydroPoly_2014'.
uw_supplemental_s: This is an archived copy of the data held at UW-Madison. For the most current data available, please visit: https://maps.washcowisco.gov/portal/apps/sites/#/maps
